{
  "page": "House Knott",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Knott</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Knott.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Knott.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4a/House_Knott.svg/250px-House_Knott.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4a/House_Knott.svg/375px-House_Knott.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4a/House_Knott.svg/500px-House_Knott.svg.png 2x\" /></a></div></div><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nA brown fret on white<br />(<i>Argent, a fret brunâtre</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\nNorth of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolfswood\" title=\"Wolfswood\">wolfswood</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountains\" title=\"Northern mountains\">northern mountains</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>The Knott</li><li>Lord Knott</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlords</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> (AGOT)</li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone\">House Baratheon of Dragonstone</a> (ADWD)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Knott</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountain_clans\" title=\"Northern mountain clans\">mountain clan</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>. In <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, the head of the mountain clan are addressed by the title \"Lord Knott\" but their clan folk call them \"The Knott\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The clan lives in the <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountains\" title=\"Northern mountains\">hills and mountains north</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolfswood\" title=\"Wolfswood\">wolfswood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#House_Knott_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Knott at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Knott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Knott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>King <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> travels to the <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountains\" title=\"Northern mountains\">northern mountains</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> gaining many clans for his <a href=\"/index.php/Fight_by_Deepwood_Motte\" title=\"Fight by Deepwood Motte\">fight by Deepwood Motte</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/index.php/March_on_Winterfell\" title=\"March on Winterfell\">march on Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Knott_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Knott at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Knott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Knott at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>There are no known Knotts mentioned during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i>.\n</p>\n<ul><li>No member 